<BaseLayout title="About">
  <article class="prose" data-reveal>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>I'm Ben Smith — a software developer with 15 years of experience building web applications, developer tools, and the occasional side project.</p>
    <p>This site is where I write about what I'm learning, building, and thinking about. Some posts are technical deep-dives, others are reflections on the craft of software. All of them are things I found interesting enough to spend time with.</p>
    <p>I believe the best interfaces are the ones that feel simple at first glance and reward you the more you use them. This site is my attempt to practice what I believe.</p>
    <p>Built with Astro, deployed on DigitalOcean. The animations are all code — no video, no CMS, just carefully crafted motion.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
